<p><img style="MARGIN: 5px 14px 7px 0px; FONT-SIZE: medium; FONT-WEIGHT: normal" border="0" hspace="8" vspace="8" align="left" src="http://admtnk.sdep.ru/images/200x200/pfr123.jpg" /> </p>
